" event pertains, *what* is one of the constants :const:`PyTrace_CALL`, "
":const:`PyTrace_EXCEPTION`, :const:`PyTrace_LINE`, :const:`PyTrace_RETURN`, "
":const:`PyTrace_C_CALL`, :const:`PyTrace_C_EXCEPTION`, "
